gameengine.model.Actions

Class Action

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameengine.model.Actions.Action
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAction
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChangeAttribute, Destroy, GlidingAction, HarmEnemy, HorizontalBounceCollision, HorizontalStaticCollision, LoseGame, MovingAction, NextLevel, VerticalBounceCollision, VerticalStaticCollision, WinGame

    public abstract class Action
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAction
    This class defines the generalized behavior of an Action object. Since the Action class is abstract, the perform function will have to be implemented in a manner specific to the type of action.

    blakekaplan
